kah","tag-forgiveness-al-maghfirah","tag-manners-adab","tag-peace-al-salam","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-seeking-forgiveness-al-istighfar","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8P9","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":738,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/28\/o-allah-you-are-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":33923,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Peace: O Allah, you are peace and from you is peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, finished his prayer, he would not sit long enough but to say,\u00a0\u201cO Allah, You are peace and from You is peace. Blessed are You, the Majestic and Noble.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 592 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/29\/tashahhud-fi-hajjah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33923,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: Testifying to faith in prayer and in need","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, taught us to bear witness to faith in prayer and to bear witness to faith in times of need. Bearing witness in prayer is to say, \u201cGreetings are for Allah, as are prayers and pure things.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2067,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/11\/tashahhud-sitting-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":33923,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: What to say when sitting in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: While praying behind the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, we were saying, \u201cPeace be upon Allah, peace be upon this person.\u201d The Prophet told us one day, \"Verily, Allah Himself is Peace. When one of you sits in prayer, let him say,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34446,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/05\/dua-forgiveness-adhan\/","url_meta":{"origin":33923,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Adhan: Supplication for forgiveness after call to prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever says when he hears the call to prayer, \u2018I testify there is no God but Allah alone, without any partner, and Muhammad is His servant and His messenger, I am pleased with Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35581,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/06\/istighfar-sujood\/","url_meta":{"origin":33923,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sujud: Ask Allah&#8217;s forgiveness in prostration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, used to say in his prostration, \u201cO Allah, forgive all of my sins, the small and large, the first and last, the public and private.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 483 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34843,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/27\/hadith-khtubah-al-hajah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33923,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Khutbah al-Hajah: How the Prophet began his sermons","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, gave us the combination of all good things and their endings, for he taught us the statements of prayer and the statements of need. The statements of prayer are, \u201cAll greetings, prayers, and good things are\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33923","targetHin